- Huwag tumigil... Huwag tumigil...

965
00:48:10,453 --> 00:48:12,663
Pupunta ako at kukunin kita.

966
00:48:14,123 --> 00:48:15,124
Napaka-asshole mo.

967
00:48:15,875 --> 00:48:19,044
<i>[Tumawa si Keifer]</i>

968
00:48:19,962 --> 00:48:23,132
<i>[Nagtatawanan sina Keifer at Ci-N]</i>

969
00:48:27,011 --> 00:48:28,053
Nakakatawa ba yun?

970
00:48:29,722 --> 00:48:30,389
<i>[Natatawa si David]</i>

971
00:48:30,390 --> 00:48:32,099
<i>[Nagsasaya ang mga lalaki]</i>

972
00:48:39,106 --> 00:48:40,106
Tumigil ka!

973
00:48:40,316 --> 00:48:41,567
Kailangan nating makaalis!

974
00:48:42,651 --> 00:48:46,197
Ito ang bagong ride na ginagawa nila.

975
00:48:46,363 --> 00:48:48,532
Kunin mo, Calix, para magawa mo
iuwi mo kay Mica.

976
00:48:48,657 --> 00:48:50,817
- Ito ay kamukha ni Mykel.
- Iyan ang iyong ina, tanga.

977
00:48:53,329 --> 00:48:54,830
Kita mo? Wala kang nabaril.

978
00:48:55,247 --> 00:48:56,749
Party! Party!
<i>[pagpapalakpak]</i>

979
00:48:59,668 --> 00:49:02,379
Takot ako sa Carousel.
Mica, mahal kita.

980
00:49:02,630 --> 00:49:04,047
- May tanong ako sayo.
- Oo?

981
00:49:04,048 --> 00:49:06,759
Ganito ba ang pakiramdam
sa tuwing iikot mo ang ulo ni Mica?

982
00:49:07,718 --> 00:49:09,010
Masaya ka ba niyan, ha?

983
00:49:09,011 --> 00:49:10,011
<i>[tumawa]</i>

984
00:49:11,138 --> 00:49:12,306
Giddy up. Giddy up.

985
00:49:12,473 --> 00:49:13,516
Wooh!

986
00:49:15,309 --> 00:49:16,685
Mama!

987
00:49:16,977 --> 00:49:17,686
<i>[Nagsisigawan ang mga lalaki]</i>

988
00:49:17,687 --> 00:49:18,771
Anak ka!

989
00:49:18,938 --> 00:49:20,397
Lalabas na ang tae ko!

990
00:49:20,814 --> 00:49:23,150
Kaya ganito pala ang pakiramdam ng mahulog!

991
00:49:23,526 --> 00:49:24,651
Para sayo.

992
00:49:24,652 --> 00:49:26,195
<i>[sumisigaw]</i>

993
00:49:26,612 --> 00:49:28,947
- Gusto kong bumaba!
- Ikaw anak ng isang asong babae!

994
00:49:28,948 --> 00:49:30,366
<i>[sumisigaw]</i>

995
00:49:33,702 --> 00:49:36,872
76, 77...

996
00:49:38,457 --> 00:49:39,457
78...

997
00:49:41,544 --> 00:49:42,962
79...

998
00:49:44,421 --> 00:49:46,172
May fireworks!

999
00:49:46,173 --> 00:49:47,258
Sobrang cool.

1000
00:49:48,968 --> 00:49:49,969
Kahanga-hanga.

1001
00:49:50,553 --> 00:49:52,930
tignan mo! Sobrang ganda.

1002
00:49:54,348 --> 00:49:55,391
Oo, sobrang ganda talaga.

1003
00:49:59,395 --> 00:50:00,395
Cliché

1004
00:50:05,693 --> 00:50:07,152
Napakagandang tanawin.

1005
00:50:10,322 --> 00:50:11,615
Sobrang cool!

1006
00:50:12,199 --> 00:50:13,909
Nakita mo ba yun?

1007
00:50:20,916 --> 00:50:23,294
Hey. Lilipat na naman kami.

1008
00:50:24,044 --> 00:50:25,129
Shit!

1009
00:50:26,922 --> 00:50:28,340
Ayaw mo bang bumaba?

1010
00:50:28,591 --> 00:50:30,341
Hindi ako nakakuha ng a
video ng fireworks!

1011
00:50:30,342 --> 00:50:31,342
Dahil sayo.

1012
00:50:35,180 --> 00:50:36,220
- Ibigay mo sa akin yan!
- Uh-uh.

1013
00:50:37,683 --> 00:50:38,809
- Ibigay mo sa akin.
- Hindi.

1014
00:50:39,059 --> 00:50:40,311
Sabi ko ibalik mo!

1015
00:50:40,936 --> 00:50:42,145
Paano kung mahulog ako?

1016
00:50:42,146 --> 00:50:43,606
Ngayon takot kang mahulog.

1017
00:50:44,189 --> 00:50:45,441
Last time, tumalon ka diba?

1018
00:50:46,025 --> 00:50:48,736
Hello? Ito ay masyadong mataas. pwede akong mamatay.

1019
00:50:48,902 --> 00:50:49,902
Huwag kang mag-alala.

1020
00:50:50,613 --> 00:50:52,031
Sasaluhin kita ulit pag nahulog ka.

1021
00:50:52,823 --> 00:50:53,824
Kaya cliché.

1022
00:50:56,619 --> 00:50:57,494
- Ibigay mo sa akin.
- Hindi.

1023
00:50:57,495 --> 00:50:59,705
Naiinis na talaga ako.
Sabi ko, ibalik mo.

1024
00:51:00,080 --> 00:51:01,206
- Ibigay mo dito!
- Hindi.

1025
00:51:01,415 --> 00:51:02,249
Ibigay mo sa akin!

1026
00:51:02,250 --> 00:51:03,584
<i>[Sumisigaw si Jay-jay]</i>

1027
00:51:04,585 --> 00:51:05,585
<i>[Tumawa si Ci-N]</i>

1028
00:51:07,004 --> 00:51:08,004
Kita mo?

1029
00:51:08,255 --> 00:51:10,049
Sabi ko sa'yo sasaluhin pa rin kita.

1030
00:51:14,094 --> 00:51:15,094
Bumaba ka na.

1031
00:51:15,721 --> 00:51:16,721
Tumigil ka.

1032
00:51:18,015 --> 00:51:19,350
Yuri, tutulungan mo ba ako?

1033
00:51:20,059 --> 00:51:21,059
Ang lalaking ito...

1034
00:51:21,393 --> 00:51:22,144
Keifer!

1035
00:51:22,311 --> 00:51:23,937
- Jay...
- Huwag! huwag!

1036
00:51:24,271 --> 00:51:24,772
huwag!

1037
00:51:25,022 --> 00:51:26,273
- Tulungan mo ako.
- Huwag.

1038
00:51:26,357 --> 00:51:27,357
- Huwag.
- Pakiusap.

1039
00:51:27,691 --> 00:51:28,233
huwag!

1040
00:51:28,525 --> 00:51:29,525
<i>[Umuungol si Jay-jay]</i>

1041
00:51:31,320 --> 00:51:32,547
Ano bang problema mo?!

1042
00:51:32,571 --> 00:51:32,946
Halika dito.

1043
00:51:33,072 --> 00:51:34,198
<i>[sumisigaw]</i>

1044
00:51:34,281 --> 00:51:35,281
<i>[Tumawa si Ci-N]</i>

1045
00:51:35,699 --> 00:51:37,493
Aray! Ang bigat mo!

1046
00:51:38,994 --> 00:51:40,411
What the hell?!

1047
00:51:40,412 --> 00:51:42,790
Ay, Yuri. Sabi ko tulungan mo ako!

1048
00:51:43,707 --> 00:51:45,041
Anong meron sa mukha?

1049
00:51:45,042 --> 00:51:46,709
Aray! Mga paa ko, Jay!

1050
00:51:46,710 --> 00:51:48,504
Bakit ka tumatawa?!
Halika at tulungan mo ako!

1051
00:51:49,254 --> 00:51:49,755
Ano ba...

1052
00:51:49,756 --> 00:51:50,838
Aray...

1053
00:51:50,839 --> 00:51:52,508
Jasper Jean Mariano!

1054
00:51:53,258 --> 00:51:54,258
Bumaba ka na!

1055
00:51:56,136 --> 00:51:57,136
Ikaw ang may kasalanan nito!

1056
00:52:09,233 --> 00:52:11,068
Sasabihin ko kay Angelo na i-ground ka!

1057
00:52:11,819 --> 00:52:14,071
Hoy! kinakausap pa kita.
saan ka pupunta

1058
00:52:14,154 --> 00:52:15,154
Sa taas!

1059
00:52:15,656 --> 00:52:18,158
Tigilan mo na yang Keifer na yan!

1060
00:52:18,325 --> 00:52:19,827
Hilahin ka lang niya kasama niya!

1061
00:52:19,993 --> 00:52:22,996
Nagkataon lang.
Kasama ko talaga sina Ci-N at David.

1062
00:52:23,163 --> 00:52:26,166
Kahit sino pa yan, hindi mo gagawin
makipag-hang out sa sinuman mula sa Seksyon E.

1063
00:52:26,625 --> 00:52:28,584
Sobra ka. Nag-iinarte ka
mas mahigpit kay Angelo.

1064
00:52:28,585 --> 00:52:29,585
sasabihin ko sayo.

1065
00:52:30,003 --> 00:52:31,088
sabi ko pasensya na.

1066
00:52:31,463 --> 00:52:33,343
Baka meron ka na
feelings for that Keifer.

1067
00:52:41,640 --> 00:52:42,641
hindi ko bibitawan.

1068
00:52:46,228 --> 00:52:47,228
Jay!

1069
00:52:57,072 --> 00:52:58,365
[Sumisigaw si Jay-jay]

1070
00:52:58,824 --> 00:53:00,409
Sabi ko sa'yo sasaluhin pa rin kita.

1071
00:53:02,202 --> 00:53:03,203
Bakit hindi ka makasagot?

1072
00:53:03,662 --> 00:53:05,873
Naramdaman mo ba talaga si Keifer?

1073
00:53:06,457 --> 00:53:08,208
baliw ka ba Ni hindi ko siya gusto!

1074
00:53:08,834 --> 00:53:09,834
Jay-jay!

1075
00:53:38,781 --> 00:53:43,535
<i>Hindi ko inaasahan na gagawin ni Denzel
nakatira sa isang lugar na tulad nito.</i>

1076
00:53:44,495 --> 00:53:45,495
David!

1077
00:53:45,954 --> 00:53:47,247
Salamat sa pagdala sa akin dito.

1078
00:53:47,456 --> 00:53:48,456
Oo naman.

1079
00:53:48,582 --> 00:53:51,782
Sinabi ko na sa iba, para pumunta na tayo
may solusyon sa problema ni Denzel.

1080
00:53:52,461 --> 00:53:54,797
Ewan ko lang kung sila
kayang gawin ito ng maaga.

1081
00:53:57,549 --> 00:53:58,549
pasensya na ha?

1082
00:53:59,468 --> 00:54:01,135
- Oh. ikaw pala.
- Nandito ba si Denzel?

1083
00:54:01,136 --> 00:54:02,136
Nasa loob siya.

1084
00:54:02,554 --> 00:54:03,554
Teka, tatawagan ko lang siya.

1085
00:54:03,639 --> 00:54:04,639
salamat po.

1086
00:54:08,143 --> 00:54:09,686
Denzel, may naghahanap sayo.

1087
00:54:20,739 --> 00:54:21,782
bakit ka nandito?

1088
00:54:26,620 --> 00:54:27,996
Kailangan kang makausap ni Jay-jay.

1089
00:54:31,208 --> 00:54:32,209
Pumunta ka. Kausapin mo siya.

1090
00:54:35,379 --> 00:54:36,630
<i>[Napangiti si Jay-jay ng awkward]</i>

1091
00:54:38,298 --> 00:54:41,552
Naiintindihan ko kung gagawin mo
husgahan ako pagkatapos kong marinig ang katotohanan.

1092
00:54:44,972 --> 00:54:46,390
Ginamit ko lang si Grace.

1093
00:54:48,851 --> 00:54:50,644
Nakikita mo ang aming lugar, tama ba?

1094
00:54:54,189 --> 00:54:55,482
Paano mo siya ginamit?

1095
00:54:56,650 --> 00:54:58,861
Nagtatrabaho ang nanay ko sa bahay nila.

1096
00:54:59,611 --> 00:55:01,738
Nakatira siya sa tita niya at mayaman sila.

1097
00:55:02,531 --> 00:55:04,658
Inggit ako sa mayayaman kaya lang...

1098
00:55:05,075 --> 00:55:07,911
Sabi ko sa sarili ko gagawin ko lahat
para maging katulad nila.

1099
00:55:10,372 --> 00:55:11,999
At ginamit mo si Grace bilang tool?

1100
00:55:12,457 --> 00:55:13,457
Nakipagkaibigan ako sa kanya.

1101
00:55:15,168 --> 00:55:18,505
Sinubukan kong maging mapaglaro sa kanya, kahit na
kahit na lagi siyang masungit sa akin.

1102
00:55:19,756 --> 00:55:21,508
Hanggang sa naging komportable na siya sa akin.

1103
00:55:23,093 --> 00:55:25,596
Niloko ko siya para makuha
nag-enroll ako sa HVIS.

1104
00:55:26,179 --> 00:55:28,390
Pagpasok ko sa school,

1105
00:55:29,808 --> 00:55:31,143
Sinimulan kong hindi pinansin si Grace.

1106
00:55:33,687 --> 00:55:34,730
Nakonsensya ako.

1107
00:55:36,899 --> 00:55:38,275
Patuloy niya akong kinakausap.

1108
00:55:38,901 --> 00:55:40,986
Patuloy akong binibigyan ng magagandang bagay.

1109
00:55:41,403 --> 00:55:43,572
Cellphone. Mga sapatos.

1110
00:55:45,157 --> 00:55:47,618
Akala ko magsasawa siya sa akin
kaya hinayaan ko na lang siya.

1111
00:55:48,660 --> 00:55:50,245
Inaani ko ang lahat ng mga benepisyo pagkatapos ng lahat.

1112
00:55:52,497 --> 00:55:55,417
Naging mag-asawa kami, pero inilihim.

1113
00:55:57,502 --> 00:55:59,755
Sinubukan kong makipaghiwalay sa kanya pero...

1114
00:56:01,632 --> 00:56:02,716
hindi ko kaya.

1115
00:56:03,508 --> 00:56:04,508
Dahil...

1116
00:56:06,553 --> 00:56:07,553
Dahil...

1117
00:56:08,096 --> 00:56:09,306
Dahil sa wakas minahal mo na siya?

1118
00:56:16,605 --> 00:56:18,357
Natatakot akong mawala siya.

1119
00:56:24,237 --> 00:56:26,657
Hindi niya ako mapapatawad
kapag nalaman niya ang totoo.

1120
00:56:31,078 --> 00:56:33,705
Gagawin ko ang lahat
managot, ngunit...

1121
00:56:34,164 --> 00:56:35,164
Pero Grace?

1122
00:56:40,963 --> 00:56:41,963
Grace?

1123
00:56:47,844 --> 00:56:49,721
<i>Naiintindihan ko ang nararamdaman ni Grace.</i>

1124
00:56:50,472 --> 00:56:54,142
<i>Mas masakit kapag ang mga salita...</i>

1125
00:56:54,601 --> 00:56:56,478
<i>ay binibigkas ng taong mahal mo.</i>

1126
00:57:02,526 --> 00:57:04,194
sinungaling ka.

1127
00:57:22,921 --> 00:57:24,089
Grace!

1128
00:57:24,381 --> 00:57:25,549
Grace!

1129
00:58:33,200 --> 00:58:34,451
- Grace!
- Grace!

1130
00:58:34,576 --> 00:58:35,868
Please, pag-usapan natin ito!

1131
00:58:35,869 --> 00:58:37,370
Wag kang lalapit sakin!

1132
00:58:37,537 --> 00:58:39,538
Tatalon ako kung lalapit ka sa akin.

1133
00:58:39,539 --> 00:58:41,165
Alam kong sanay ka nang manakit ng iba.

1134
00:58:41,166 --> 00:58:43,710
Pero kahit yung mahal mo,
gusto mong masaktan?

1135
00:58:44,294 --> 00:58:46,880
Pinatay nila siya, Jay. Namatay siya!

1136
00:58:47,130 --> 00:58:49,216
Lahat kayo gustong iligtas si Grace!

1137
00:58:49,299 --> 00:58:51,551
Pero paano ang kapatid ko? ha?

1138
00:58:51,718 --> 00:58:53,637
Walang nangahas na iligtas siya!

1139
00:58:53,845 --> 00:58:55,679
Lumabas ka talaga sa iyo
paraan para makapunta dito, ha?

1140
00:58:55,680 --> 00:58:58,307
kausapin mo ako. Okay, galit ka kay Aries.

1141
00:58:58,308 --> 00:59:00,602
Pero bakit kailangan
magalit din sa akin?

1142
00:59:00,769 --> 00:59:03,422
Pwede bang tumigil ka na sa pakikialam
sa buhay ng ibang tao?

1143
00:59:03,447 --> 00:59:05,366
Keifer! Keifer!

1144
00:59:05,440 --> 00:59:06,983
Ano ba yang sinisigawan mo?

1145
00:59:07,275 --> 00:59:09,193
- Ito ay Jay-jay!
- Anong nangyari kay Jay-jay?

1146
00:59:09,194 --> 00:59:11,613
Si Ram naman. Hindi ko sila nakita, pero sigurado ako!

1147
00:59:11,696 --> 00:59:13,240
Jay!

1148
00:59:13,448 --> 00:59:14,616
Hi, boys!

1149
00:59:15,075 --> 00:59:17,494
ano? Na-miss ako?

1150
00:59:17,953 --> 00:59:19,079
Nasaan si Jay-jay?!

1151
00:59:19,412 --> 00:59:20,956
Tinawag ni Ram si Kiko!

1152
00:59:21,123 --> 00:59:23,332
Sigurado akong nahuli siya
sa gulo mo na naman!

1153
00:59:23,333 --> 00:59:25,961
Babatukan ko sila
kung hinawakan nila siya! I swear!

1154
00:59:26,128 --> 00:59:27,878
Teka, tanungin muna kita.

1155
00:59:27,879 --> 00:59:29,131
Gusto mo ba si Jay-jay?

1156
00:59:29,548 --> 00:59:30,882
Nahuhulog na yata ako sa kanya.

